It's a way to insert a component (like a compressors, reverb components, etc.) directly inline with a preamp by using a single 1/4" jack.

Easy Connection: 6.35mm(1/4 inch) TRS jack connector have 360 degree easy-grip treads for frequent unplugging and durability. It splits closer to the 1/4 jack ends, the distance to the split point is 9.8 inchs(25cm) .The red connector is for the right channel and the blue connector is for the left channel.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: ZTOXLR 1/4 inch TRS Stereo Y-Splitter Insert Cable Product features: 1/4 TRS Stereo to Dual 1/4 TS Mono Insert Cable Y-Splitter Cable,This Insert cables are used for creating a real-time effects loop by connecting a channel insert on an audio mixing board to an external effects processor with 1/4" unbalanced connections.Connect the TRS plug into the "insert" jack of your mixing board. The tip of the jack is a send (sending a mono signal to an external effects professor) and the ring is the return (returning a mono signal from the external effects processor back into the mixing board). This cable can also be used to split an unbalanced stereo signal into two unbalanced mono signals, or to combine two mono signals into a single stereo signal.Professional Audio Transmission Cable is focusing on the production of high-quality professional-grade audio transmission cables and provides quality services. With wide range of using scenarios, professional audio cables are made of premium oxygen-free copper. The materials offer you reliable quality, ensuring excellent sound transmission.

ZTOXLR 1/4 TRS Stereo to Dual 1/4 Mono Cable This insert cable is designed for providing a real-time effects by connecting a channel insert onto audio mixing control board to external audio processor with 1/4" unbalanced connections.The Tip of TRS connector is for transmitting mono signal to external audio professor and the Ring of TRS connector is for receiving mono signal back into mixing control board. It can be also applied to split an unbalanced stereo signal into two unbalanced mono signals or to combine two mono signals into a single stereo signal.Compatible with Preamps, Amplifiers, and more devices equipped with a 1/4" TRS jack. Premium metallic case which makes it easily withstand everyday usage. Connecting your portable audio devices to loudspeaker system, sound cards, PA audio, Mixer and more devices.

High-performance 1. Gold-Plated Metal Pins2. Removable Housing3. Rugged Metal Connector 24K Gold Plated for better sound quality and less loss Dual Insulated shielded insulated copper conductor (Oxygen Free Copper), extra large quantities of braided copper inside, resist the interference EMI or RF from outside. Applicability Wide range of applications: Can be used on personal equipment such as Laptop, Phone,Tablet, MP3 and so on; and professional audio equipment such as mixers, amplifiers, stereos, etc.
